     "name": "question9",
     "maxWidth": "600px",
     "html": "<p><br /></p><h4 style=\"text-align:left\"><b>C. Do I have to give my permission for certain specific uses?</b></h4><p></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;color:black;font-size:16px\">Yes. The following information will only be released if you give your specific permission by putting your initials on the line(s).</p>"
